{"tid":717780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《侏羅紀》基因恐龍不是夢    古生物學家：最快 5 年後誕生","createTime":"2018-06-26T09:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T10:41:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":95,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"476e98bc757ab01c19bb5b916cd0d3863c895264","tid":717780,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"著名古生物學家，兼《侏羅紀》系列電影恐龍顧問 Dr. Jack Horner 指出，他們的團隊能夠在未來 5 到 10 年内培養出基因恐龍。他們採用的方法跟電影中不同，不是從蚊子中提煉出恐龍血液，而是在雀鳥的基因上「加工」。由於很多科學家相信雀鳥是恐龍的遺傳後代，所以他們認爲修復雀鳥基因，就能「創造」出已經滅絕的恐龍。<br />\n<br />\n而的確，這個哈佛耶魯組成的團隊已經成功改寫雀鳥基因，讓雀鳥的鳥嘴部份長得像恐龍的口鼻。接下來就是讓翅膀變回恐龍手臂、手；將恐龍尾巴變回來？誰知道呢。團隊指出，整個研究最難的部分，就是「創造」出失蹤的尾巴，但他們已經離「創造恐龍」十分接近。<br />\n<br />\n另外，團隊還嘗試從「雞」著手研發恐龍，並成功創造出「Chickenosaurus」的物種。如果順利的話，也許大家在 5 年後就能見到由雞基因創造出來的完整恐龍呢！然而隨之而來的道德、觀念衝擊究竟會導致什麽後果，就很難説了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2099394/zhuluoji4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2099394%2Fzhuluoji4_600.jpg&h=e122edcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2099394/%E3%80%8A%E4%BE%8F%E7%BE%85%E7%B4%80%E3%80%8B%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%81%90%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A2%EF%BC%81%E5%8F%A4%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB+5+%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2099394%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E4%25BE%258F%25E7%25BE%2585%25E7%25B4%2580%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2581%2590%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A2%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%258F%25A4%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB%2B5%2B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%2594%259F&d=xBUnGN%2F33Zh0ziXbQfL0yttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=63b43956\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2099394/%E3%80%8A%E4%BE%8F%E7%BE%85%E7%B4%80%E3%80%8B%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%81%90%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A2%EF%BC%81%E5%8F%A4%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB+5+%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbb0e8b627fc875ecfec581e1bad8a24f56b30b","tid":717780,"uid":101390,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"準備變Jurassic World<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba76465305b71185f4a45e84c716f79db5b4e2e","tid":717780,"uid":152123,"like":135,"dislike":7,"score":128,"quote":{"pid":"cfbb0e8b627fc875ecfec581e1bad8a24f56b30b","tid":717780,"uid":101390,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"準備變Jurassic World<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"睇完電影都唔識死嘅科學怪人"},{"pid":"5112b211911c7b3a5ab99e2740a210eea7cad97a","tid":717780,"uid":184679,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/mFs2uTo9WKs/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FmFs2uTo9WKs%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=587cb668&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eefac1a67c54f09eb46db0f8a4730e9e9ab4352","tid":717780,"uid":67551,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"快啲啦<br />\n等到變廢中都未有"},{"pid":"22b59aa4cbd33672064173f2cbff2ab8a876f1c1","tid":717780,"uid":153807,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/184054_3925413d5569fc1864649bc356301ec2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%